init_text: An alien has kidnapped Matt Damon, not knowing what lengths humanity goes through to retrieve him whenever he goes missing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien has taken Matt Damon to his home planet, which is very similar to Earth.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien has no idea what he has gotten himself into, and the humans have no idea what they are getting themselves into.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien and Matt Damon were able to escape, and they are now on the run from the humans.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The humans would believe him, and the alien would be safe.
